===============================================================================
  MAC4 Coprocessor Speedup Report
  PicoRV32 + PCPI 4-way INT8 MAC Accelerator
  Generated from Icarus Verilog simulation logs
===============================================================================

Architecture
------------
  CPU core      : PicoRV32 (rv32im)
  Coprocessor   : picorv32_pcpi_mac  (opcode 0x2B, custom1)
  Operation     : 4-way packed int8 multiply-accumulate
  Simulation    : Icarus Verilog (behavioral)

Neural Network
--------------
  Model         : TinyCNN for MNIST (int8 quantized)
  Conv2D        : 1 input ch -> 4 filters, 3x3 kernel, ReLU
  MaxPool2D     : 2x2, stride 2
  FC (Dense)    : 676 -> 10
  Test set      : 10 pre-loaded sample images (digits 0-9)

